node.text:
We watched “fatherhood” and was crazy good movie hit home Bc I was raised by single father too S.O pops @kevinnishi wouldn’t be here without u. 

Korean corndogs
1 ¼ cup flour
½ ts salt & sugar
1 tb baking powder
1 egg
¾ cup milk
Hotdogs
Mozzarella 
Panko breadcrumbs

Tteokbokki
6 cup hondashi 6 TB gochujang 
2 TB red pepper flakes & sugar
2 to soysauce
Scallions
Mozzarella cheese (shredded)
Rice cakes 2lbs 
(We made large batch half the recipe of using less)***

#koreancorndogs #tteokbokki #moviemonday #datenight #cookingvideo #koreanfood

node.text:
This the best easiest Kung pao chicken you will ever make no 🧢

Ingredients

Onion
Red bell pepper
garlic
Dry chilli flakes
Chilli whole dry
Chicken thighs
Soy sauce
Sesame oil
Sugar
5 spice
Corn starch
cashews

Instructions

PREP: Onion sliced, red/yellow pepper chopped, zucchini chopped, 1 TB minced garlic,
Crushed cashews

Debone the chicken thighs and cut up into whatever size pieces u want, its ur food, i kept skin on

Chicken marinade: 1 TB Sugar, 1 ts rice vinegar, 2 TB soy sauce, ½ ts sesame oil, pinch five spice 2 TB cornstarch

Now shallow fry the chicken in BATCHES if u want the best outcome, if time is shmoney then do it all at once like ya boy, 5-6 mins its quick, set side on paper towel lined plate

Empty oil leaving a little bit and add onion, garlic, and 1-2 TB chilli flakes and/or dry whole chillis sliced depending on how spicy u want urs

Then add the rest of prepped veg, add 2 TB soy, 1 TB sugar, 1 TB oyster sauce,

Once veg softened add the chicken back, 

Cashews (optional)

Serve @ a safe distance

#cookingvideo #howtocook #asianfood #kungpaochicken

node.text:
Katsu SANDO 🥵🐥

Easy to make a must try 👩‍🍳

Ingredients 
- chicken thigh
- Panko
- egg
- hot sauce
- Japanese mayo
- paprika salt pepper garlic powder
- frying oil 
- white bread

Instructions 
Prep: flatten & debone thighs if not boneless already, shred / slice cabbage thin, make spicy Mayo (add fav hot sauce to Japanese Mayo)

Coating: 3 steps:
Corn starch dredge egg wash panko
Season all of them generously & hit egg wash with hot sauce
- then chicken goes dredge > eggwash > panko >> then fry til golden brown 3-4 mins

Lightly toast bread then build sando chicken, cabbage, spicy mayo

Then to be extra cut into 3 & enjoy

Easy anybody can make it!

#katsusando #chickenkatsu #friedchicken #japanesefood

We watched “fatherhood” and was crazy good movie hit home Bc I was raised by single father too S.O pops @kevinnishi wouldn’t be here without u. 

Korean corndogs
1 ¼ cup flour
½ ts salt & sugar
1 tb baking powder
1 egg
¾ cup milk
Hotdogs
Mozzarella 
Panko breadcrumbs

Tteokbokki
6 cup hondashi 6 TB gochujang 
2 TB red pepper flakes & sugar
2 to soysauce
Scallions
Mozzarella cheese (shredded)
Rice cakes 2lbs 
(We made large batch half the recipe of using less)***

#koreancorndogs #tteokbokki #moviemonday #datenight #cookingvideo #koreanfood

node.text:
Rays Koumandra soup (Tom Yum) 🍲 

This movie I fw it heavy the message behind it is some real shiiit 🎥 

Ingredients
Shrimp
Galangel
Lemongrass
Limes
Fish sauce
Nam prik pow
Cilantro
Thai chillies
Cilantro
Roma tomato
White onion
Oyster mushrooms
Shrimp paste

Instructions
Prep: peel shrimp keep shells & heads, crush & cut lemongrass, slice glangel
Boil the shrimp shells 10 mins then strain
Add shrimp heads
Galangel(or ginger)

Add mushrooms, 1lb peeled shrimp
& raya kounamdra ingredients
1 TB Shrimp paste from tail
¼ cup Bamboo shoot
4 Chilies
⅓ cup Palm sugar from heart
4tb Lemongrass

Serve up add some rice if you like 🍚 
Idk how this supposed to be eaten but flips add rice to soup so Issa mover

Mini Calzones 🍕 

Don’t sleep on cooking dates try this. But even if u single u should try these calzones so EZ 👩‍🍳 

Easy pizza dough
- 2 cups flour
- 3/4 cup water
- 1 pack instant yeast
- 1/2 TB salt & sugar
- 1TB olive oil

Knead 10 mins and rest for 30 

#calzone #dateidea #pizza #howtocook #howtomakecalzones #cookingvideo

node.text:
Fish & Chips 🐠 🥔 

Actually heat

Ingredients
Beer
Baking soda
Flour
Starch
White fish (cod)
Vodka

Instructions
Prep for fish batter
Batter:  flour, corn starch, salt, season garlic powder, paprika - beer until it is smoothie consistency 
Dredge: flour corn starch, salt, season garlic powder paprika

Now season fish with salt >> dredge >> batter >> fry few mins till golden brown and crispy

Fries could use frozen fries or homemade
Homemade - russet potatoes cut into fries
and we will double fry but only in one batch, for 4 mins fry it in oil (Ned heat) then go hi heat and fry till golden brown and crispy
Tar tar sauce
½ C Mayo
½ lemon juice
2 dill pickles diced
Splash hot sauce
salt & pepper

Serve 

#fishchips #beerbatter #fish
